                        <summary><p>Gaṅgājaṭādhara temple of Govindapputtūr. Begins on the westernmost wall section of the northern façade and continues on the northernmost wall section of the western façade. Regnal year 14 of Kōpparakesarivarman = Uttamacōḻa (<foreign>circa</foreign> 985 C.E.). The translation of this inscription is given p. 68.</p>
                            
